videos.description: The Aces are the first ones to a loose ball, and it ends up with Angel McCoughtry knocking down the jumper.

tracking.trackingName: WNBA_One-Play (Aces' hustle leads to a McCoughtry jumper) 2020/07/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Aces' hustle leads to a McCoughtry jumper

videos.description: Angel McCoughtry finds a running A'ja Wilson, who finishes the layup to cap off Vegas' 10-0 run to start the second half.

videos.description: Allie Quigley knocks down a tough 3-pointer, giving the Sky the lead with less than 20 seconds remaining.

videos.headline: Quigley drains game winner for the Sky
